        <name>Facet-id8gah99c7g</name>
        <type>Facet</type>
    </flexiPageRegions>
    <flexiPageRegions>
        <itemInstances>
            <componentInstance>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>decorate</name>
                    <value>true</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;1) &lt;strong&gt;SMART Objectives.&lt;/strong&gt; There are several definitions. For R3 Digital this means …&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specific &lt;/strong&gt;- be as specific as possible with the desired objective. Generally, the more specific an objective is, the clearer the steps to achieving it will be&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Measurable&lt;/strong&gt; - aim to agree on an objective that can be evidenced to track progress/ confirm completion. If an objective cannot be directly measured, it may be appropriate to agree a suitable proxy&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Achievable&lt;/strong&gt; - ensure the objective is realistic and possible to complete or maintain within the agreed time. Objectives should be challenging - do not avoid agreeing stretch objectives, but note them as such&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Relevant&lt;/strong&gt; - make sure the objective aligns with the values and goals of the organisation. The alignment may come through a direct cascade of the annual objectives, or may reference a capability build or other strategic alignment&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Timebound&lt;/strong&gt; - make sure the goal is set within an appropriate time frame. Typically the objective will be defined within the review year (May to April) but the agreed outcome could be short-term (i.e. specified within the year). Longer-term objectives should be considered for breaking into interim milestones that can be measurably achieved in-year&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2) &lt;strong&gt;R3 Digital Values.&lt;/strong&gt; SMART objectives can be “What” or “How” objectives but can tend to be focussed on the “What”. Our values set an overarching context for who we are and how we behave ..&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Success &lt;/strong&gt;- We are committed to, and celebrate customer, team and individual success&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Innovation &lt;/strong&gt;- We are a team of creative, capable and forward-thinking experts&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaboration &lt;/strong&gt;- Our relationships are consultative, flexible and positive&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Trust &lt;/strong&gt;- We build credibility and respect by being inclusive, reliable and transparent&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pride &lt;/strong&gt;- We believe that taking care of the details drives high-quality outcomes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentName>flexipage:richText</componentName>
                <identifier>flexipage_richText</identifier>
            </componentInstance>
        </itemInstances>
        <name>Facet-q55e90jzdr</name>
        <type>Facet</type>
    </flexiPageRegions>
    <flexiPageRegions>
        <itemInstances>
            <componentInstance>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>decorate</name>
                    <value>true</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Annual Performance Expectations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Suggest around 4 - 6 annual SMART performance objectives (see Appendices) - certainly no more than 8. Select a FY Quarter that you expect to achieve the expectation by.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Annual Personal Developmnt Expectations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Suggest around 1 - 3 annual SMART performance objectives (see Appendices) - certainly at least 1. Select a FY Quarter that you expect to achieve the expectation by.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expectations of R3 Digital to Support Performance &amp;amp; Personal Objectives&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drafted by individual and agreed with line manager - any items that the individual is looking for from the line manager or wider R3 Digital in order to succeed with their individual performance and personal development objectives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This could include training, insights, mentoring or requests around ways of working. The objective here is to initiate an open discussion between individual and organisation around their expectations of the organisation in order to support the agreed outcomes above.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The line manager will take a judgement call around those expectations they are able to commit to, and those that might need agreement or awareness from others in R3.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentName>flexipage:richText</componentName>
                <identifier>flexipage_richText3</identifier>
            </componentInstance>
        </itemInstances>
        <name>Facet-d98daa45-1c2c-4098-832f-e55e411f4204</name>
        <type>Facet</type>
    </flexiPageRegions>
    <flexiPageRegions>
        <itemInstances>
            <componentInstance>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>decorate</name>
                    <value>true</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Individual Comments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drafted by the individual, ideally before the half-year review with the line manager - a short text summary of progress against objectives, assistance required to overcome challenges.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The 6-month review is also an opportunity to review whether the objectives need additions, or amendments in agreement based on new insights or context.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Specific actions agreed in the half-year review may be documented here&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reviewer Comments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Completed by the line manager during or after the half-year review with the individual, a short commentary on progress.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Any changes to the annual objectives (additions, removals, changes to measures or timing) agreed at the 6-month review should be signed-off by the line manager here.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Specific actions agreed in the half-year review may be documented here&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentName>flexipage:richText</componentName>
                <identifier>flexipage_richText4</identifier>
            </componentInstance>
        </itemInstances>
        <name>Facet-3dfd8a26-2e57-4a07-b828-9a38fb7a02b7</name>
        <type>Facet</type>
    </flexiPageRegions>
    <flexiPageRegions>
        <itemInstances>
