                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Individual Comments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drafted by the individual, before the end of year review with the line manager - a short text summary of progress against objectives and general comments on performance and development over the year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note the individual should also draft the end of year review status against the performance and development objectives in the table above - this input will form the basis for the individual/line manager conversation and agreement. The individual should expect that the line manager will challenge the proposed end of year status against the SMART objectives.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Individual comments may be amended in the end of year review on agreement between individual and line manager - comments should only be shared outside of that conversation once they have been agreed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ideas or actions for next year may be suggested here, but should be formalised in the following years Expectations Exchange&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;360 Feedback&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drafted by the individual, before the end of year review with the line manager - a short text summary of feedback on line manager support as well as wider R3 Digital performance to the individuals expectations over the year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Line manager feedback is essential to improve team performance and should be welcomed by all line managers. It is against our R3 Digital values to be defensive when offered feedback from team members.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Individuals comments may be amended in the end of year review on agreement between individual and line manager - comments should only be shared outside of that conversation once they have been agreed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reviewer Comments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Completed by the line manager during or after the end of year review with the individual, a short summary of progress against objectives and general comments on performance and development over the year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Reviewer comments may be amended after the end of year review on agreement between individual and line manager - comments should only be shared outside of that conversation once they have been agreed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ideas or actions for next year may be suggested here, but should be formalised in the following years Expectations Exchange&lt;/p&gt;</value>
